The 6 . 6 magnitude quake hit steep hills of China ' s southwestern Sichuan province . The earthquake occurred at 8 : 02 am local time ( 0002 GMT ) in Lushan county and the epicentre had a depth of 13 km ( 8 miles ), state news agency Xinhua reported . China ' s Twitter - like Sina Weibo micro - blogging service was abuzz with earthquake hitting the country .